     "The recognizer, the fixer, the equivalence, and the fixtype.")

    (xdoc::li
     "Several theorems about the recognizer, fixer, and equivalence."))

   (xdoc::p
    "See the implementation, which uses a readable backquote notation,
     for details.")))

